      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NULLA OUR PRIZE (2) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when third (23.03) at Ballarat in a Rank Limit - Restricted Win. Good beginner aided by a handy draw. Better than latest and can atone here. CADILLAC SNOOP (8) has been close to a win, finishing in the minors four on end before a fourth when checked in the run last time in a Grade 6/MDN at this track (18.89). Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Better than latest and worth another try. PICK A CADILLAC (6) produced a moderate run last time when fifth at this track over 305m behind Canya Guru (18.74) in a Grade 6/MDN. Has good speed so he should be prominent despite the draw. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. NULLA WILLIAM (4) jumps at a shorter journey and still warrants respect.",
